<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=716&amp;p=744#p744"><![CDATA[
4/9(Sun.) Plastic wet wipes ban planned in England to tackle pollution/Baboon's death after two-week hunt sparks outcry in Taiwan(Host: Danny)<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />Session 1:<br />7:05-7:40 pm<br />Individual Presentation<br />7:40-8:00<br />Group discussion.<br />Session 2.<br />8:00-8:40 pm<br />Individual<br />8：40-9:00 pm<br />Group discussion.<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br />Article1: Plastic wet wipes ban planned in England to tackle pollution<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-65166859">https://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-65166859</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Discussion<br />1. What is your opinion on the distribution of plastic particles mentioned in this article on Earth?<br />2. This article mentions some solutions to environmental pollution. Which solutions do you think are most promising and why?<br />3. What public policies in your city can promote sustainable development and reduce environmental pollution?<br /><br />Article2: Baboon's death after two-week hunt sparks outcry in Taiwan<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-65096467">https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-65096467</a><!-- m --><br />Discussion<br />1. What are your thoughts on the killing of this baboon? Do you believe hunting activities should be restricted?<br />2. The incident has sparked a lot of anger and protests. Do you think this kind of reaction is appropriate?<br />3. How do you think this incident will affect Taiwan's image and tourism industry?<br />4. How do you think humans and wild animals should coexist? What can we do to balance protecting wild animals and meeting human needs?<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Thu Apr 06, 2023 11:16 pm</p><hr />
